public class IssueSubmitFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements IIssueSubmitListener

A UI for adding issues to a Mantis site.

The program may either be started without any argument or with the three arguments <url> <user> <password>.

Author:
Peter Lanser, planser@users.sourceforge.net
